river-adventure-house.jpg.description: The whale is a blue decorative figure positioned at the top of the yellow water slide, situated in the upper left area of the image.

construction-evening.jpg.description: The person riding a horse is located on the top right side of the image, near the trees under the night sky. The horse is brown, and the rider is wearing an orange shirt.
The castle is located in the top right corner of the image. It is set on a hill and is surrounded by trees, with a crescent moon and a star in the sky.

kf-winter.jpg.description: The sun is located in the upper right corner of the image. It is a small, orange circle against the light grayish sky, adding a warm contrast to the snowy scene.

The log cabin is located in the lower left section of the image. It's a rectangular structure with a green roof and light brown walls. There are people standing outside, engaged in various activities.
